      <title>美联储鲍威尔准备支持就业市场，即使这意味着通胀挥之不去</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-24/fed-s-powell-ready-to-support-job-market-even-if-inflation-lingers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着 2022 年通胀飙升，美联储通过提高利率来防止工资螺旋式上涨。现在，随着失业率小幅上升，央行发出降息信号，以阻止裁员螺旋式上升 — — 即使这意味着一段时间内通胀会有所上升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-24/fed-s-powell-ready-to-support-job-market-even-if-inflation-lingers</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 16:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
